Modules
=======
- add INSMOD -> insert module
 - this will include the requested acrm file
	for example:
	- file: qt.acrm
	- <contents>
		add_flag....
		ENVWORDS="${ENVWORDS} FOO BAR"
	- </contents>
	- acr will check if the requested file exists, (local dir, share dir)
	- documentation required.


